SELENIUM-4 features :

1. Capture, Monitor & Mock the network requests & responses.
2. Inject session cookies and perform basic Auth .
3. Mock device coordinates for Mobile/Tab views.
4. Check the monitor the site's performance
5. Mock geolocations of users 
6. Block the network requests 
7. Mock faster / slower netwrk speeds.
8. Execute and debug javaScript . 

//whatever the chrome devtools do the above tasks from browsers , the same
tasks we can also do now using selenium4 by writing automated script 

